   <title>
    九巴推55元「旅客日票」涉逾450條路線 稱能對香港留下好印象
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%8E%A855%E5%85%83%E3%80%8C%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A5%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%8D%E6%B6%89%E9%80%BE450%E6%A2%9D%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-%E7%A8%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%A5%BD%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1
