   <title>
    有店家推真「盲盒壽司」 老闆：大家開心
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%97%E5%AE%B6%E6%8E%A8%E7%9C%9F%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%92%E5%A3%BD%E5%8F%B8%E3%80%8D-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83
   </link>
   <description>
    <![CDATA[<div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-18 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">內容: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/lifestyle">生活</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F202404253.jpg" width="940" height="492" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-19 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">自由標籤: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/528473">獨媒報導</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539225">盲盒壽司</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/506737">壽司</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/534024">管制即棄塑膠</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><font color="#e4692b">【獨媒報導】</font>4月22日起正式推行第一階段管制即棄膠餐具措施，除「紙羮」等替代餐具質素引起爭議外，一張DON DON DONKI「盲盒壽司」的照片亦在網上引起熱話。「大嘥鬼」昨晚「解畫」，稱堂食打包即屬外賣，食肆可提供膠杯及膠盒，惟事件已一發不可收拾。有店家推真盲盒壽司「抽水」，老闆坦言「無錢賺」，只為大家開心。</p>
<p>推出就真盲盒壽司的是「千之味刺身壽司專門店」，一盒10件壽司承惠$98。老闆阿樂指會有海膽、吞拿魚等貴價貨，亦戲言或會出現10件白飯，「唔開嗰一刻你都唔知自己今晚食乜」。他表示帖文刊出後，有約10位客人購買，亦有人預訂，惟明言只為「抽水」，並無錢賺，「反正周圍都靜，有樣野大家接受到、又開心，就當宣傳」，將推出一段時間。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/DuSx9y6HbY" title="75bd6626-58f9-4dfe-9285-729a8df0cd48"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53677229933_0cab10360b_b.jpg" alt="75bd6626-58f9-4dfe-9285-729a8df0cd48" /></a><br /><em>「千之味刺身壽司專門店」Facebook圖片</em></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/92b751Sb87" title="IMG_7207"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53677366199_117043d6a1_b.jpg" alt="IMG_7207" /></a><br /><em>「千之味刺身壽司專門店」Facebook圖片</em></p>
<p>第一階段管制即棄膠餐具日前實施，禁止銷售和免費供應受管制即棄塑膠產品，包括禁止在堂食及向外賣顧客提供膠叉、膠刀、膠匙、膠飲管等餐具。阿樂由於壽司多以筷子進食，首階段亦未涵蓋外賣膠盒，影響不大，主要是外賣不再提供豉油膠盒，並改配木匙等餐具。他明言更「害怕」垃圾徵費，料每月額外開支達3,000元，「根本就係搶錢，佢地啲大財團梗係無所謂，對我地鋪仔黎講係好大負擔」，形容政策不知民間疾苦。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/D0v9350sF2" title="IMG_7205"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53677229893_b03171ff97_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="IMG_7205" /></a><br /><em>「千之味刺身壽司專門店」Facebook圖片</em></p>
</div></div></div>]]>
